  "body": "### Problem description\n\nRight now when we have an aggregation duty at epoch n, we'll subscribe to the 1st slot of epoch `n-1` which force us to process a lot of attestations unnecessarily\r\n\r\ncc @dapplion \n\n### Solution description\n\nInvestigate a good value (`x` slot) to subscribe to subnet in advance\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
